high_descs: Turn right and head towards the bread on the counter.
Pick up the bread from the counter.
Turn right and head towards the fridge next to the microwave.
Open the fridge, place the bread on the second shelf, let it cool, and take it out from the fridge.
Turn left and head towards the sink.
Place the bread behind the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the bread to place it on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the counter to your right, near the sink.
Pick up the bread loaf next to the knife.
Go to the fridge next to the counter.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Turn left and go to the counter near the sink.
Place the bread on the counter, to the right of the pepper.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on a counter.

high_descs: turn right to face the kitchen counter next to the sink
place the bread inside the fridge to cool, then take it back out
walk over to the kitchen sink
place the bread on top of the counter next to the sink
